      "title": "👑 Pixaroma - Note - START HERE",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW  \n\n---\n\n### Put all models in the models folder, organized into their respective subfolders. \n### If a required folder doesn’t exist, create it.\n\n---\n\n\n## 🟣 Load Diffusion Model\n### Download the model **flux-2-klein-9b-kv-fp8.safetensors** ~9.1GB from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-klein-9b-kv-fp8/resolve/main/flux-2-klein-9b-kv-fp8.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/flux2` \n\nLearn More about this model [HERE](https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-klein-9b-kv-fp8)\n \n---\n\n## 🟣 Load CLIP\n\n###  Download **qwen_3_8b_fp8mixed.safetensors**  from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux2-klein-9B/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_8b_fp8mixed.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders`  \n\n--- \n\n## 🟣 Load VAE\n\n### Download the **flux2-vae** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux2-dev/resolve/main/split_files/vae/flux2-vae.safetensors)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Nodes Installed from Manager  \n\n-\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma)  \n💬 **Community Discord:** [Join Here](https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3)\n"
      ],
